Step 1: Check if pip for python2 is installed. If not
	sudo apt-get install python-pip
Step 2:  Install telepot package for python2
	sudo pip install telepot
Step 3: Read telegrambot.py using
	nano telegrambot.py
Step 4: Insert the api token in place of 'Bot Token' in the telegrambot.py
	 bot = telepot.Bot('Bot Token') 
Step 5: Run the code with
	python2 telegrambot.py